casebody.data:
Tuesday, April 23, 1991

MOTION DOCKET

91-713. State, ex rel. Serge, v. Clermont Cty. Court of Common Pleas, Div. of Domestic Relations.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition. Upon consideration of relator’s motion for alternative writ and request for oral argument, IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion and request be, and the same are hereby, denied.

Sweeney, J., dissents as to the denial of the motion for alternative writ.
